high_descs: Turn right then walk forward head to the sink
Pick up the fork in the sink
Turn left then face the left cabinet below the coffee maker
Open the cabinet put in the fork in the green container
Pick up the green container then close the cabinet
Look up the counter beside the stove
Put the container with fork on the counter beside the green apple
anns.task_desc: Put the container with fork on the counter

high_descs: Go to fridge, turn right.  Proceed to sink on right.  Turn right to face sink.
Pick up fork from sink, to the right of the green sponge.
Turn left, go to wall, turn left to face counter with coffee maker.
Open cabinet under counter, put fork in cup to the left of the cabinet.
Pick up fork in cup from cabinet, close cabinet doors.
Look up to face counter.
Place cup with fork on counter front and to the left of the apple and coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Pick up fork, put in cup in cabinet, pick up both and put on counter.

high_descs: Turn and go to the sink.
Pick up the fork that is on the right in the sink.
With the fork in hand turn and go to the coffee maker
Open the cabinets that are below the coffee maker and place the fork inside the green cup in the cabinet.
Pick up the green cup with the fork in it.
Lift up so you are now facing the counter top.
Place the green cup with the fork on the counter in front of and to the left of the green apple.
anns.task_desc: Place the fork with green cup on counter.
